OL,5,Coperations
OL,7,FA surgeon who performed artificial
OL,8,Fmesh operations unnecessarily on more
OL,9,Fthan 200 patients at two hospitals in
OL,10,FBristol has been struck off the
OL,11,Fmedical register.
OL,13,FAnthony Dixon was found to have left
OL,14,Fpatients in agony following bowel
OL,15,Fsurgery at the Southmead and Spire
OL,16,FHospitals.
