OL,4,Cpatients in agony from 'mesh'
OL,5,Coperations
OL,7,FMr Dixon denied the claims against him
OL,8,Fin two separate tribunals but the
OL,9,FMedical Practitioners Tribunal Service
OL,10,Fhearing (MPTS) ordered his removal
OL,11,Ffrom the medical register.
OL,13,FAllegations about his conduct first
OL,14,Farose 8 years ago.
OL,16,FHe was one of the UK's leading
OL,17,Fsurgeons based at Southmead Hospital
OL,18,Fand Spire Hospital in Bristol where
OL,19,Fhe'd pioneered the use of artificial
OL,20,Fmesh to treat prolapsed bowels.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
