OL,3,CSurgeon struck off after leaving
OL,4,Cpatients in agony from 'mesh'
OL,5,Coperations
OL,7,FOver the two medical tribunals, it
OL,8,Femerged that he had failed to gain
OL,9,Finformed consent to operate on five
OL,10,Fpatients and acted dishonestly by
OL,11,Ffabricating patients' records long
OL,12,Fafter his involvement in their care.
OL,14,FThree years ago a review by Southmead
OL,15,FHospital found more than 200 patients
OL,16,Fwere operated on unnecessarily and
OL,17,Fdozens were left in agony.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
