OL,5,Coperations
OL,7,FOne former patient Paula Goss says she
OL,8,Fwas left unable to work and
OL,9,Ftraumatised after Dixon's surgery but
OL,10,Fshe welcomed the news.
OL,12,FShe said: "I'm really, really pleased
OL,13,Fwith the sanction that was given.
OL,15,F"Striking him off was the only thing
OL,16,Fthey could have done with regards to
OL,17,Fwhat he'd done to many patients,
OL,18,Fincluding myself.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
