OL,5,Coperations
OL,7,F"I've suffered for many years since
OL,8,F2014 - still suffering now - and it is
OL,9,Fsomething that many of the patients
OL,10,Fhave had to go through and we
OL,11,Fshouldn't have had to have gone
OL,12,Fthrough."
OL,14,FAnthony Dixon has always denied the
OL,15,Fallegations but has previously
OL,16,Fapologised for his misconduct and the
OL,17,Fpain that his patients have endured
OL,18,Fsince.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
