OL,5,Coperations
OL,7,FYet this latest tribunal found there
OL,8,Fhad been "a serious departure" from
OL,9,Fthe standards expected from a doctor
OL,10,Fand his dishonesty was "premeditated
OL,11,Fand sustained".
OL,13,FDixon had been suspended for more than
OL,14,Fa year - but today he was struck off
OL,15,Fand will not practice medicine again.
